## Escalation

If turnaround slips past 2 business days or the counterparty refuses DocuSign, escalate to the **Legal Operations lead** per Policy §5. Any deviation from the two mandatory execution steps requires written approval from the **General Counsel** documented in Ironclad (Policy §10).
